<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="F" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Feathered" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Feathered,</orth> 1) furnished with feathers: <cit><quote>f. wings,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ven 306" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 306</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>breasts,</quote> <bibl n="shak. luc 1122" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 1122</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>creatures,</quote> <bibl n="shak. son 143.2" default="NO" valid="yes">Sonn. 143, 2</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. pht 11" default="NO" valid="yes">Phoen. 11</bibl>.<lb />2) winged: <cit><quote>f. Mercury,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 4.1.106" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A IV, 1, 106</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>Cupid,</quote> <bibl n="shak. oth 1.3.270" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. I, 3, 270</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>in f. briefness,</quote> <bibl n="shak. per 5.2.15" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. V, 2, 15</bibl></cit>.
